messages.text: Why do you ask? Would you like me to answer no?
I want to know because I'm your MOTHER
Why do you always have to think the worst of me?
Could you please let me know something about your life from time to time?
We're fine. I'm getting good grades in college.
I have a two weeks break next month...
Do you think a Florida trip would do me good?
Mom I don't want you to come here and judge me
Just let me live my life
You remember where you left it?
Do you still hear the steps?
At the far end of the pic, on the right
Isn't that your car under the exit sign?
But if I go he'll catch me
I don't think there's anyone there
I'm telling you there is someone!!
Don't tell me I'll be fine you have no idea!
Sorry I'm just trying to help
I got to my car and drove off
But I saw her in the rear view mirror
But that's crazy! Why would she?
Cos she wants to put me away!! Obviously!
She was wearing a mask like this
How do you know it was her is she was wearing a mask?
Just wanted to know how you were doing
I haven't seen you around in a while. Miss you!
I realised I don't want to be a doctor
I'm not interested in a college education
I want to be a stay home wife
Oh that's cool! You're getting married then?
Yeah in a couple of weeks
Not a lot of women are brave enough to make that decision anymore
I'm having a small party at my place on Saturday
Would you and Matthew like to come?
Do you prefer to wait for him at home? :)
To get his dinner ready and stuff
Most girls wouldn't think like that
I'm just saying people aren't always ready to make efforts in relationships
Relationships aren't always perfect but if you love someone you've got to prove it
Is it like that for you and Matthew?
Had you ever thought of giving up your studies before you met him?
No but now I know it's what I want
Men need women to support them, don't they?
By the way I have no classes tomorrow morning, fancy a cup of coffee in town?
Don't think I can tomorrow, sorry
We're doing some renovation work in our apartment
You really deserve such a loving relationship
It's not luck, you deserve it!
We should all give love and respect and deserve the same
You can really tell when you're in a good relationship, right?
Your world becomes bigger, more hopeful!
You feel like you're truly yourself and you're free to do what you really want
You sure you can't come out for a bit, after dinner?
Sorry now is not a good time
I can't leave the house right now
